=== 發展與融資 ===
此電影前提是由電影製片人{{link-en|琳達·奧布斯特|Lynda Obst}}及理論物理學家[[基普·索恩|基普·索恩]]構思的，他們於1997年的電影《[[超時空接觸|超時空接觸]]》已經合作，並在天文學家[[卡爾·薩根|卡爾·薩根]]給他們速配時已互相認識<ref name="jolin">{{cite journal | last=Jolin | first=Dan | title=The Ultimate Trip | journal=[[Empire_(magazine)|Empire]] | date=November 2014 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wired.com/2014/10/astrophysics-interstellar-black-hole/|title=How Building A Black Hole For 'Interstellar' Led To An Amazing Scientific Discovery - Wired|work=WIRED|access-date=2014-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171216204440/https://www.wired.com/2014/10/astrophysics-interstellar-black-hole/|archive-date=2017-12-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。二人基於索恩的科研工作上構思兩個方案，關於「在宇宙中最奇異的事情是突然讓人類可以接觸得到」，這吸引到電影製片人[[史提芬·史匹堡|史提芬·史匹堡]]執導的興趣<ref>{{cite news | last=Fernandez | first=Jay A. | url=http://articles.latimes.com/2007/mar/28/entertainment/et-scriptland28 | title=Writer with real stars in his eyes | work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] | date=2007-03-28 | accessdate=2014-05-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171114160124/http://articles.latimes.com/2007/mar/28/entertainment/et-scriptland28 | archive-date=2017-11-14 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。電影於2006年6月開始研製，當時史匹堡跟派拉蒙電影公司宣布由琳達·奧布斯特與基普·索恩撰寫八頁的關於一部科幻電影的計劃。奧布斯特在電影的附著上，[[綜藝雜誌|綜藝雜誌]]指在史提芬·史匹堡執導之前，是「需要幾年才能走到一起」<ref>{{cite journal | last=Fleming | first=Michael | url=http://variety.com/2006/film/news/space-chase-pic-on-par-launch-pad-1200337693/ | title=Space chase pic on Par launch pad | journal=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | date=2006-06-14 | accessdate=2014-10-01 | author= | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180129004705/https://variety.com/2006/film/news/space-chase-pic-on-par-launch-pad-1200337693/ | archive-date=2018-01-29 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="news.sciencemag.org">{{cite web|url=http://news.sciencemag.org/people-events/2014/11/physicist-who-inspired-interstellar-spills-backstory-and-scene-makes-him|title=Physicist who inspired Interstellar spills the backstory—and the scene that makes him cringe|publisher=|access-date=2014-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151026153855/http://news.sciencemag.org/people-events/2014/11/physicist-who-inspired-interstellar-spills-backstory-and-scene-makes-him|archive-date=2015-10-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在2007年3月，[[強納森·諾蘭|強納森·諾蘭]]被聘請為一部電影撰寫劇本，題為《星際效應》<ref>{{cite news | last=Fernandez | first=Jay | url=http://articles.latimes.com/2007/mar/24/entertainment/et-quick24.6 | title=Spielberg, Nolan plan sci-fi project | work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] | date=2007-03-24 | accessdate=2014-10-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305150151/http://articles.latimes.com/2007/mar/24/entertainment/et-quick24.6 | archive-date=2016-03-05 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

由於史匹堡於2009年把他的工作室[[夢工場|夢工場]]從[[派拉蒙|派拉蒙]]移至[[華特迪士尼影業集團|華特迪士尼影業集團]]，所以派拉蒙需要新導演為《星際效應》執導。[[基斯杜化·路蘭|基斯杜化·路蘭]]建議他的弟弟[[強納森·諾蘭|強納森·諾蘭]]於2012年參與該項目。強納森·諾蘭與基普·索恩會面，然後擔任執行製片人去討論故事中的[[時空|時空]]。2013年1月，派拉蒙與[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]宣布與基斯杜化·路蘭洽談為《星際效應》執導<ref>{{cite journal | last=Sneider | first=Jonathan | url=http://variety.com/2013/film/news/nolan-in-talks-for-interstellar-1118064459/ | title=Nolan in talks for 'Interstellar' | journal=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | date=2013-01-09 | accessdate=2014-10-01 | author= | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170524003317/http://variety.com/2013/film/news/nolan-in-talks-for-interstellar-1118064459/ | archive-date=2017-05-24 | dead-url=no }}</ref> 。他指自己希望鼓勵[[載人航天|載人航天]]的目標<ref name="fritz">{{cite news | last=Fritz | first=Ben | url=http://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2014/07/24/director-christopher-nolan-causes-a-stir-while-promoting-interstellar-at-comic-con/ | title=Director Christopher Nolan Causes Stir While Promoting 'Interstellar' at Comic-Con | work=[[Wall_Street_Journal|Wall Street Journal]] | date=2014-07-24 | accessdate=2014-07-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140726220236/http://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2014/07/24/director-christopher-nolan-causes-a-stir-while-promoting-interstellar-at-comic-con/ | archive-date=2014-07-26 | dead-url=no }}</ref>，並打算根據他自己的想法，與他們弟弟合併寫一個劇本<ref>{{cite news | last=Fleming | first=Mike | url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/01/the-migratory-habits-of-800-pound-gorilla-oscar-directors-and-the-films-they-make/ | title=The Migratory Habits Of 800-Pound Gorilla Oscar Directors And The Films They Make | publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] | date=2013-01-10 | accessdate=2013-08-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130901175052/http://www.deadline.com/2013/01/the-migratory-habits-of-800-pound-gorilla-oscar-directors-and-the-films-they-make/ | archive-date=2013-09-01 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。隨後到三月，基斯杜化·路蘭落實為《星際效應》執導，這將會在他的製作公司{{link-en|先厥電影公司|Syncopy Inc.}}與{{link-en|琳達·奧布斯特|Lynda Obst}}的{{link-en|琳達·奧布斯特製作公司|Lynda Obst Productions}}旗下製作<ref>{{cite journal | last=Hayden | first=Erik | url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/official-christopher-nolans-interstellar-be-426889 | title=It's Official: Christopher Nolan's 'Interstellar' to be Warner Bros., Paramount Co-Production | journal=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] | date=2013-03-08 | accessdate=2014-10-01 | author= | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170914133853/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/official-christopher-nolans-interstellar-be-426889 | archive-date=2017-09-14 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[荷李活速報|荷李活速報]]指路蘭的酬金是二千萬美元，而非電影銷售額的20%，約$121萬美元<ref>{{cite journal | author=Staff | url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/hollywood-salaries-revealed-movie-stars-737321 | title=Hollywood Salaries Revealed, From Movie Stars to Agents (and Even Their Assistants) | journal=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] | date=2014-10-02 | accessdate=2014-10-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141026034254/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/hollywood-salaries-revealed-movie-stars-737321 | archive-date=2014-10-26 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。為了研究電影的拍攝，路蘭參觀了[[美國太空總署|美國太空總署]]以及私營的航天公司[[太空探索科技公司|太空探索科技公司]]。

雖然派拉蒙和華納兄弟傳統上是競爭對手的工作室，華納兄弟發行了路蘭的{{link-en|蝙蝠俠電影|The Dark Knight Trilogy}}，並跟他的公司先厥電影公司尋求諾蘭於派拉蒙製作《星際穿越》的股份。華納兄弟同意給派拉蒙共同資助下一部電影《[[五月十三日|五月十三日]]》，及電視連續劇《[[南方公園|南方公園]]》改編的電影
的權利。華納兄弟公司也同意讓派拉蒙共同出資，作為「一個有待確定的華納A-list資產」<ref>{{cite journal | last1=Kit | first1=Borys | last2=Masters | first2=Kim | url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/christopher-nolans-interstellar-warner-bros-562879 | title=Warner Bros. Gives Up 'Friday the 13th' Rights to Board Christopher Nolan's 'Interstellar' | journal=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] | date=2013-06-05 | accessdate=2014-10-01 | author= | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612163726/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/christopher-nolans-interstellar-warner-bros-562879 | archive-date=2018-06-12 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年8月，[[傳奇電影公司|傳奇電影公司]]最終審定了跟華納兄弟達成協議，資助電影約25%的製作，雖然無法延續其與華納兄弟公司約8年的合作生產夥伴關係，據報導，傳奇電影同意放棄《[[蝙蝠俠對超人：正義曙光|蝙蝠俠對超人：正義曙光]]》的融資計劃，以換取《星際效應》的股份<ref name="galloway20130814">{{cite journal | last1=Siegel | first1=Tatiana | last2=Galloway | first2=Stephen | url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/legendary-scores-christopher-nolans-interstellar-605010 | title=Legendary Scores Christopher Nolan's 'Interstellar' in Warner Bros. Divorce | journal=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] | date=2013-08-14 | accessdate=2014-10-01 | author= | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107124753/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/legendary-scores-christopher-nolans-interstellar-605010 | archive-date=2017-11-07 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 編寫與選角 ===
[[File:Dust-storm-Texas-1935.png|thumb]][[德克薩斯州|德州]]北部的一場[[沙塵暴|沙塵暴]]，為[[1930年代|1930年代]]北美[[黑色風暴事件|黑色風暴事件]]的一部分。以此為主題的紀錄片《{{link-en|黑色風暴|The Dust Bowl (film)}}》為後來電影的場景設定提供了題材]]
編劇[[強納森·諾蘭|強納森·諾蘭]]被史匹堡聘為《星際效應》編寫劇本，史匹堡為此已努力了四年的時間<ref>[Jolin, Dan (November 2014). "The Ultimate Trip". Empire]</ref>。為了要了解科學的理論，他在寫劇本期間到[[加州理工學院|加州理工學院]]研究[[相對論|相對論]]<ref>{{cite AV media | series = Larry King Now | publisher = Ora TV | title = What Does A Showrunner Bring To A Deserted Island? | medium = Television production | url = https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QD1Bj1egE3U | date = 2014-04-15 | accessdate = 2014-05-27 | format =  | time = 3:48 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161129222721/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QD1Bj1egE3U | archive-date = 2016-11-29 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。強納森說他對航天飛機計劃，以及[[美國太空總署|美國太空總署]]是如何缺乏資金支持[[載人火星任務|載人-{火星任務}-]]也持悲觀態度。編劇在一些[[科幻電影|科幻電影]]找到靈感，如[[太空奇兵·威E|太空奇兵·威E]]（2008）及[[阿凡達|阿凡達]]（2009）。《[[娛樂周刊|娛樂周刊]]》評論指：「他把內容設定在一個被枯萎病蹂躪的反烏托邦未來社會，但頑強的民族都不屈服於絕望。<ref name="jensen">{{cite journal | last=Jensen | first=Jeff | url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2014/10/16/interstellar-christopher-nolan-anne-hathaway/ | title=Inside 'Interstellar,' Christopher Nolan's emotional space odyssey | journal=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] | date=2014-10-16 | accessdate=2014-10-16 | author= | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141017144424/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2014/10/16/interstellar-christopher-nolan-anne-hathaway/ | archive-date=2014-10-17 | dead-url=no }}</ref>」強納森的哥哥，導演[[基斯杜化·路蘭|基斯杜化·路蘭]]，他曾研究其他科幻電影劇本，但在繁多的劇本之間，決定採用《星際效應》的劇本，選擇由喬納森和基普·索恩提出的想法，在他把自己努力多年的劇本合併之前，挑選他覺得他作為導演可以得到「傳達給觀眾，希望不會失去他們」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/interstellars-christopher-nolan-stars-gather-742727|title='Interstellar's' Christopher Nolan, Stars Gather to Reveal Secrets of the Year's Most Mysterious Film|author=Stephen Galloway|work=The Hollywood Reporter|access-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107124756/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/interstellars-christopher-nolan-stars-gather-742727|archive-date=2017-11-07|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2014/11/10/christopher-nolan-uncut-on-interstellar-ben-affleck-s-batman-and-the-future-of-mankind.html|title=Christopher Nolan Uncut: On 'Interstellar,' Ben Affleck's Batman, and the Future of Mankind|work=The Daily Beast|access-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170507135149/http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2014/11/10/christopher-nolan-uncut-on-interstellar-ben-affleck-s-batman-and-the-future-of-mankind.html|archive-date=2017-05-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。導演克里斯多福在首個小時保持強納森的意念，它設置於未來[[資源枯竭|資源枯竭]]的地球，這個靈感源自[[美國|美國]]於1930年代[[經濟大蕭條|經濟大蕭條]]期間的[[黑色風暴事件|黑色風暴事件]]。克里斯多福反而修改了劇本，改為一隊人進入太空。看過2012年的紀錄片《{{link-en|黑色風暴|The Dust Bowl (film)}}》為靈感，他聯絡該電影的導演[[肯·伯恩斯|肯·伯恩斯]]及製片人戴頓·鄧肯（Dayton Duncan），請他們允許用於電影的專題採訪<ref name="burns">{{cite web|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/news/act-four/wp/2014/11/06/how-ken-burns-surprise-role-in-interstellar-explains-the-movie/|title=How Ken Burns' surprise role in 'Interstellar' explains the movie|work=The Washington Post|first=Alyssa|last=Rosenberg|date=2014-11-06|accessdate=2014-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171108162500/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/act-four/wp/2014/11/06/how-ken-burns-surprise-role-in-interstellar-explains-the-movie/|archive-date=2017-11-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2013年4月，決定由[[馬修·麥康納|馬修·麥康納]]和[[安·海瑟薇|安·海瑟薇]]作為電影的主演<ref>{{cite news | last=Fleming | first=Mike | url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/04/anne-hathaway-to-star-with-matthew-mcconaughey-in-christopher-nolans-interstellar/ | title=Anne Hathaway To Star With Matthew McConaughey in Christopher Nolan's 'Interstellar' | publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] | date=2013-04-09 | accessdate=2013-08-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130818025834/http://www.deadline.com/2013/04/anne-hathaway-to-star-with-matthew-mcconaughey-in-christopher-nolans-interstellar/ | archive-date=2013-08-18 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。導演克里斯多福·诺兰說，在他看過麥康納於2012年電影《[[泥土_(電影)|泥土]]》中的塑造後就對他產生了興趣<ref name="mcclintock">{{cite journal | last=McClintock | first=Pamela | url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/cinemacon-christopher-nolan-talks-interstellar-691456 | title=CinemaCon: Christopher Nolan Talks 'Interstellar,' Plugs Film Over Digital in Hollywood Reporter Q&A | journal=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] | date=2014-03-26 | accessdate=2014-03-27 | author= | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171222130734/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/cinemacon-christopher-nolan-talks-interstellar-691456 | archive-date=2017-12-22 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。他表示麥康納的角色就像個普通人，且會遇到「一般觀眾可能會遇到的故事」<ref>{{cite journal | last=McClintock | first=Pamela | url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/cinemacon-christopher-nolan-talks-interstellar-691456 | title=CinemaCon: Christopher Nolan Talks 'Interstellar,' Plugs Film Over Digital in Hollywood Reporter Q&A | journal=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] | date=2014-03-26 | accessdate=2014-04-11 | author= | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171222130734/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/cinemacon-christopher-nolan-talks-interstellar-691456 | archive-date=2017-12-22 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。演員[[伊凡·卡漢|伊凡·卡漢]]拒絕了參與本片的演出，因為他比較想出演印度電影《[[美味情書|美味情書]]》和《{{link-en|行動日|D-Day (2013 film)}}》<ref>{{cite news | last=Vyavahare | first=Renuka | url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/nri/cinema/Why-Irrfan-missed-out-on-a-Christopher-Nolan-film/articleshow/21975274.cms | title=Why Irrfan missed out on a Christopher Nolan film | work=[[The_Times_of_India|The Times of India]] | date=2013-08-22 | access-date=2014-09-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140802125841/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/nri/cinema/Why-Irrfan-missed-out-on-a-Christopher-Nolan-film/articleshow/21975274.cms | archive-date=2014-08-02 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。而[[麥特·戴蒙|麥特·戴蒙]]則在2013年8月底左右客串出演本片，並拍攝了他在冰島的戲份。

由派拉蒙、华纳和传奇影业联合制作，派拉蒙负责北美發行，华纳负责海外发行。2013年8月在[[加拿大|加拿大]][[亞伯達省|亞伯達省]]开拍。片中大约有70分鐘IMAX攝影機拍攝之画面，在IMAX影廳（70mm IMAX影廳，不含數位IMAX影廳）能獲得完整的展開效果。[[加州理工学院|加州理工学院]]物理学家[[基普·索恩|基普·索恩]]参与了剧本创作，他对[[虫洞|虫洞]]和[[时间旅行|时间旅行]]的研究为本片增添了不少科学依据。诺兰御用艺术指导{{link-en|內森·克勞利|Nathan Crowley}}表示，剧情还涉及[[黑洞|黑洞]]原理、[[相对论|相对论]]和[[万有引力|万有引力]]等许多科学概念。摄影师是《[[諜影行動|諜影行動]]》的摄影师{{link-en|霍伊特·范·霍特玛|Hoyte van Hoytema}}，而非诺兰的御用摄影师[[華力·普菲斯特|華力·普菲斯特]]，剪辑师是诺兰的老搭档{{link-en|李·史密斯 (編輯)|Lee Smith (editor)|李·史密斯}}，[[汉斯·季默|汉斯·季默]]五度为诺兰作品配乐。<ref >{{cite web |url=http://ent.163.com/14/0731/07/A2FERTOH000300B1.html |language= |title=诺兰"星际穿越"发预告 麦康纳海瑟薇踏神秘外星 |publisher=Mtime时光网 |date=2014-07-31 |accessdate= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140801174901/http://ent.163.com/14/0731/07/A2FERTOH000300B1.html |archive-date=2014-08-01 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

=== 科學指导 ===
[[基普·索恩|基普·索恩]]擔任本電影科學顧問，確保蟲洞、相對論等盡可能地準確。他表示他們討論了如何描繪蟲洞和黑洞，然後計算了容許光線穿過蟲洞或圍繞黑洞的方程式，因此觀眾看見的是建基於愛因斯坦的相對論方程式<ref name="ThorneWormhole">{{cite news|url=http://www.slashfilm.com/final-interstellar-trailer/|title=New 'Interstellar' Trailer Goes Deep; Plus Kip Thorne Featurette|date=2014-10-01|work=/Film|accessdate=2014-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141005045759/http://www.slashfilm.com/final-interstellar-trailer/|archive-date=2014-10-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在設計蟲洞和巨型旋轉黑洞時，索恩與視覺效果總監和三十名電腦特技人員合作。索恩向特技人員提供理論方程式，由他們按方程式編寫新的電腦特技軟件以造出準確的重力模擬。<ref name="wired">{{cite news|url=http://www.wired.com/2014/10/astrophysics-interstellar-black-hole/|title=WRINKLES IN SPACETIME: The Warped Astrophysics of Interstellar|date=2014-10-23|work=Wired|accessdate=2014-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171216204440/https://www.wired.com/2014/10/astrophysics-interstellar-black-hole/|archive-date=2017-12-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>

導演[[克里斯多福·諾蘭|克里斯多福·諾蘭]]最初擔心合乎科學準確度的黑洞對觀眾而言未必能夠理解，而有可能需要不合理地改變外觀，但最後認為只要他維持一致的拍攝角度就能讓效果可被觀眾理解<ref name="dailymail">{{cite news|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sciencetech/article-2805131/Does-new-film-Interstellar-realistic-black-hole-Movie-s-special-effects-result-important-scientific-discovery.html|title=Does new film Interstellar have the most realistic black hole EVER? Movie's special effects may result in important scientific discovery|date=2014-10-24|work=The Daily Mail|accessdate=2014-10-25|archive-url=https://archive.is/20141025072833/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sciencetech/article-2805131/Does-new-film-Interstellar-realistic-black-hole-Movie-s-special-effects-result-important-scientific-discovery.html|archive-date=2014-10-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由於黑洞體積巨大，質量相對極小的人類得以進入[[事件視界|事件視界]]而不會發生[[麵條化|麵條化]]現象。蟲洞於劇中也非[[二維空間|二維空間]]之洞穴而是[[三維空間|三維空間]]之球體。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.space.com/27701-interstellar-movie-science-black-holes.html|title=The Science of 'Interstellar': Black Holes, Wormholes and Space Travel|work=Space.com|access-date=2014-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160110154219/http://www.space.com/27701-interstellar-movie-science-black-holes.html|archive-date=2016-01-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>

於早期製作中，索恩立下了原則：不能違反現有[[物理定律|物理定律]]，一切想像均須有科學根據而非單憑編劇的想像。諾蘭在不影響電影製作的前提下接受這個原則。索恩曾一度花費兩星期時間遊說諾蘭放棄一個關於角色超越光速飛行的理念，他也表示能夠容許最大藝術自由的是劇中角色到訪之一個星球的冰雲層<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.sciencemag.org/people-events/2014/11/physicist-who-inspired-interstellar-spills-backstory-and-scene-makes-him|title=Physicist who inspired Interstellar spills the backstory—and the scene that makes him cringe|publisher=|access-date=2014-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151026153855/http://news.sciencemag.org/people-events/2014/11/physicist-who-inspired-interstellar-spills-backstory-and-scene-makes-him|archive-date=2015-10-26|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.npr.org/2014/11/07/362351960/christopher-nolan-on-blending-reality-into-fantasy-in-interstellar|title=For Christopher Nolan, Making 'Interstellar' Was A Childhood Dream|date=2014-11-07|work=NPR.org|access-date=2014-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160221123402/http://www.npr.org/2014/11/07/362351960/christopher-nolan-on-blending-reality-into-fantasy-in-interstellar|archive-date=2016-02-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 评论 ==

=== 专业影评 ===
在[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]网站收集到的308篇评论中，有219條正面評價、89條負面，電影的“新鮮度”为71%，觀眾支持度85%，平均分數為7（最高10）。該網站共識写道：「《星際效應》代表著更驚心-{}-動魄、令人深思，並在觀影視覺上是部燦爛的電影，這有些來自於編劇兼導演的克里斯多福·諾蘭的期望，即使它的思想衝擊力超過一定程度的把握」<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/interstellar_2014/ | title=Interstellar | work=rottentomatoes.com | publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] | accessdate=2014-11-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150812044014/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/interstellar_2014/ | archive-date=2015-08-12 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]的46篇评论中，有35條評論為正面、10條褒贬不一、1條負面，得分为74（滿分100），表明“总体好评”<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/interstellar | title=Interstellar Reviews | work=metacritic.com | publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] | accessdate=2014-11-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170804225550/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/interstellar | archive-date=2017-08-04 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。据《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》报道，電影評論家大多認為「《星際效應》是一個有娛樂性、情感和發人深省的科幻傳奇故事，縱使它會有些沉悶和感傷。」<ref>{{cite news | last=Gettell | first=Oliver | url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/moviesnow/la-et-mn-interstellar-movie-reviews-critics-20141105-story.html | title='Interstellar' is an ambitious, imperfect sci-fi epic, reviews say | work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] | date=2014-11-05 | accessdate=2014-11-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141108052023/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/moviesnow/la-et-mn-interstellar-movie-reviews-critics-20141105-story.html | archive-date=2014-11-08 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 其它評論中的科學謬誤 ===
雜誌《[[商业内幕|商業內幕]]》評論員Kirsten Acuna指出電影有四個不合理之處：庫珀尋獲太空總署秘密基地時被捕受盤問，但不久即被總署指出是它們的唯一希望，認為總署應有太空人名單而且理應能於更早時間與庫珀聯絡；庫珀於進入黑洞後身處一個連接小時候墨菲書架的五維空間，認為這設定過於天馬行空；歸鄉是庫柏在整齣電影的生存動力，結尾部分與女兒墨菲只作約兩分鐘短暫重逢後，隨即出發作另一旅程。庫珀的兒子湯姆數十年來多次傳送視訊給他甚至使他落淚，但最後完全沒有打聽兒子下落<ref>[http://www.businessinsider.com/interstellar-plot-holes-2014-11 3 'Interstellar' Plot Holes That Make No Sense] {{Wayback|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/interstellar-plot-holes-2014-11 |date=20141113081929 }}{{en}}</ref>。Mashable評論員Christina Warren指出黑洞的[[吸積盤|吸積盤]]並不合乎科學：其釋出之高能量[[X射線|X射線]]本應燒毀了太空船和船員<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mashable.com/2014/11/08/science-of-interstellar/?utm_campaign=Feed%3A+Mashable+(Mashable)&utm_cid=Mash-Prod-RSS-Feedburner-All-Partial&utm_medium=feed&utm_source=feedburner|title=Why scientists are in a love-hate relationship with 'Interstellar'|author=Christina Warren|date=2014-11-08|work=Mashable|access-date=2014-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141111182144/http://mashable.com/2014/11/08/science-of-interstellar/?utm_campaign=Feed:+Mashable+(Mashable)&utm_cid=Mash-Prod-RSS-Feedburner-All-Partial&utm_medium=feed&utm_source=feedburner|archive-date=2014-11-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。劇中沒有明確提及該吸積盤由甚麼組成；釋出的光線顏色也本應因為[[多普勒效應|多普勒效應]]而有所不同<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.skyandtelescope.com/astronomy-news/interstellar-science-fiction-science-fantasy-1107143/|title=Interstellar: Science Fiction or Science Fantasy?|work=Sky & Telescope|access-date=2014-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141217040836/http://www.skyandtelescope.com/astronomy-news/interstellar-science-fiction-science-fantasy-1107143/|archive-date=2014-12-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。中國[[上海交通大学|上海交通大学]]物理与天文系的王斌教授表示“接近[[黑洞|黑洞]]，就会被黑洞的[[潮汐力|潮汐力]]撕得粉碎，任何东西都不例外。男女主角在靠近黑洞的行星上，这个靠近的概念是多远的距离？就算靠近黑洞到可以感受到黑洞的作用，一旦越过[[事件視界|视界]]，你也就无法再返回。”<ref >{{cite web |url=http://news.163.com/14/1114/09/AB0IK47N00014AED.html |language= |title=看《星际穿越》前，需要做哪些功课 |publisher=东方早报 |date=2014-11-14 |accessdate= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141121111842/http://news.163.com/14/1114/09/AB0IK47N00014AED.html |archive-date=2014-11-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 票房 ==
=== 北美 ===
《星際效應》只有在某些限定地區提前釋出，在美國和加拿大影院選擇在11月4日下午8:00上映，這與2014年美國參議院選舉同期推出<ref>{{cite web | url = http://wwws.ww.warnerbros.com/interstellar/releasedates/ | title = WORLDWIDE RELEASE DATES | publisher = ''Warner Bros.'' | accessdate = 2014-11-07 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141016191339/http://wwws.ww.warnerbros.com/interstellar/releasedates/ | archivedate = 2014-10-16 }}</ref>。影片票房1.35萬美元榮登次日週三的首位（其中包括週二晚上的總值），從249間影院（其中有42間是觀賞IMAX銀幕）中IMAX版佔公司總毛利的62％<ref>{{cite web | url = http://deadline.com/2014/11/interstellar-big-hero-6-box-office-1201274335/ | title = ‘Interstellar’ Reports Grosses Before Weekend Showdown Against ‘Big Hero 6′ | author = Anita Busch | publisher = Deadline.com | date = 2014-11-06 | accessdate = 2014-11-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141106065800/http://deadline.com/2014/11/interstellar-big-hero-6-box-office-1201274335/ | archive-date = 2014-11-06 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。有240間影院播放35mm、70mm和IMAX70mm的電影格式<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2014/11/06/wednesday-box-office-chris-nolans-interstellar-earns-1-4m-in-limited-release/ | title = Box Office: Chris Nolan's 'Interstellar' Earns $1.35M Wednesday | author = Scott Mendelson | publisher = ''Forbes'' | date = 2014-11-06 | accessdate = 2014-11-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141107081050/http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2014/11/06/wednesday-box-office-chris-nolans-interstellar-earns-1-4m-in-limited-release/ | archive-date = 2014-11-07 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。這部電影在週四深夜賺了350萬，週二至週四的特映共計490萬美元<ref>{{cite web | url = http://deadline.com/2014/11/interstellar-big-hero-6-box-office-1201274335/ | title = ‘Interstellar’ & ‘Big Hero 6′ Off To Strong Box Office Starts – Thursday B.O. | author = Anita Busch | publisher = Deadline.com | date =2014-11-07| accessdate = 2014-11-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141106065800/http://deadline.com/2014/11/interstellar-big-hero-6-box-office-1201274335/ | archive-date = 2014-11-06 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2014/11/07/box-office-interstellar-nabs-3-5m-thursday/ | title = Box Office: 'Interstellar' Nabs $3.5M Thursday, Has $4.9M Heading Into Weekend | author = Scott Mendelson | publisher = ''Forbes'' | date = 2014-11-07 | accessdate = 2014-11-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141107220446/http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2014/11/07/box-office-interstellar-nabs-3-5m-thursday/ | archive-date = 2014-11-07 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://variety.com/2014/film/news/box-office-big-hero-6-1-4-million-thursday-previews-1201350585/ | title = Box Office: ‘Interstellar,’ ‘Big Hero 6′ Soar in Thursday Previews | author = Dave MacNary | publisher = ''Variety'' | date = 2014-11-07 | accessdate = 2014-11-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141110013013/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/box-office-big-hero-6-1-4-million-thursday-previews-1201350585/ | archive-date = 2014-11-10 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

美国首周末收4700万美元次于[[迪士尼|迪士尼]]动画片《[[大英雄天团|大英雄天团]]》居亚军，其中IMAX银幕产出1340万超过25%，也超越了《[[饥饿游戏2：星火燎原|饥饿游戏2：星火燎原]]》的1260万。<ref >{{cite web |url=http://news.mtime.com/2014/11/10/1533783-3.html#content |language= |title="超能陆战队"北美击败"星际穿越" |publisher=时光网 |date=2014-11-10 |accessdate= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141110054232/http://news.mtime.com/2014/11/10/1533783-3.html#content |archive-date=2014-11-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>次周末收2919万列第三。第三周末收1510万蝉联第三。第四周末收1580万列第四，四周累计1.47亿。

=== 國際 ===
本片於11月5日在[[法國|法國]]和[[比利時|比利時]]發行，在這兩個地區的市場佔了50％的份額，成為前五名的電影之一。在26日首次亮相在法國，來自750個螢幕就獲得了74萬3000美元<ref>{{cite web | url = http://variety.com/2014/film/news/interstellar-tops-wednesday-box-office-with-1-4-million-1201349630/ | title = ‘Interstellar’ Tops Wednesday Box Office With $1.4 Million | author = Brent Lang | publisher = 'Variety'' | date = 2014-11-06 | accessdate = 2014-11-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141107153917/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/interstellar-tops-wednesday-box-office-with-1-4-million-1201349630/ | archive-date = 2014-11-07 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.thewrap.com/interstellar-rockets-to-top-in-france-in-first-overseas-box-office-test/ | title = ‘Interstellar’ Rockets to Top in France in First Overseas Box-Office Test | author = Todd Cunningham | publisher = ''The Wrap'' | date = 2014-11-06 | accessdate = 2014-11-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141107091115/http://www.thewrap.com/interstellar-rockets-to-top-in-france-in-first-overseas-box-office-test/ | archive-date = 2014-11-07 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://m.screendaily.com/5079683.article | title = Interstellar set to rule weekend | author = Jeremy Kay | publisher = ''Screen Daily'' | date = 2014-11-06 | accessdate = 2014-11-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141107172509/http://m.screendaily.com/5079683.article | archive-date = 2014-11-07 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。這部電影於11月6日主要發行在超過35個市場，如[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]、[[澳大利亞|澳大利亞]]和[[巴西|巴西]]，並獲得了870萬美元總額。最高的首映票房是來自於[[韓國|韓國]]的480萬美元（1090個大螢幕）<ref>{{cite web | url = http://deadline.com/2014/11/interstellar-international-box-office-results-1201277313/ | title = ‘Interstellar’ Ahead Of ‘Gravity’ In Opening Bow – International B.O. | author = Anita Busch | publisher = Deadline.com | date = 2014-11-07 | accessdate = 2014-11-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141108014330/http://deadline.com/2014/11/interstellar-international-box-office-results-1201277313/ | archive-date = 2014-11-08 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

